            <h3>What is Endless Runner?</h3>
            <p>Endless Runner is an exciting side-scrolling action game where you control a character running through an endless landscape. Your goal is to survive as long as possible by avoiding obstacles, collecting coins, and using power-ups while being chased by a relentless monster.</p>

            <h3>Game Objectives</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Survive:</strong> Avoid obstacles and water pits to stay alive</li>
                <li><strong>Collect Coins:</strong> Gather as many coins as possible to increase your score</li>
                <li><strong>Use Power-ups:</strong> Collect special items to gain temporary advantages</li>
                <li><strong>Set Records:</strong> Achieve high scores and climb the leaderboard</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Controls</h3>
            <div class="highlight">
                <strong>Space Bar:</strong> Jump (double jump available)<br>
                <strong>S Key or Down Arrow:</strong> Slide/Crouch<br>
                <strong>Canvas Click:</strong> Jump (mobile/touch devices)
            </div>

            <h3>Obstacles & Challenges</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Ground Obstacles:</strong> Rocks and barriers that must be jumped over</li>
                <li><strong>Flying Birds:</strong> Aerial enemies that require sliding under or jumping over</li>
                <li><strong>Gaps:</strong> Deadly water pits that must be jumped across</li>
                <li><strong>Fire Traps:</strong> Flaming obstacles that activate periodically</li>
                <li><strong>Pendulums:</strong> Swinging axe traps with complex movement patterns</li>
                <li><strong>Ropes:</strong> Wide gaps with ropes that can be crossed by holding the space bar</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>Power-ups</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>üõ°Ô∏è Shield:</strong> Temporary invulnerability (7 seconds)</li>
