                <li><strong>üí∞ Double Coins:</strong> Score multiplier for collected coins (7 seconds)</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>The Monster</h3>
            <p>A relentless pursuer that gets closer with each obstacle you hit. After 3 obstacle hits within 10 seconds, the monster becomes deadly and can catch you. Strategic platforming and power-up usage can help you survive longer.</p>

            <h3>Scoring System</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Coins:</strong> 1 point each</li>
                <li><strong>Distance:</strong> Tracked in pixels traveled</li>
                <li><strong>Survival Time:</strong> Duration of successful runs</li>
                <li><strong>Difficulty Level:</strong> Increases every 75 points</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

